cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically the problem of 6D object pose estimation. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests cs.LG (Machine Learning) as a likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel approach to dealing with occlusions, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.GR (Graphics).
